清咁勁咁清楚<br />\n<br />\n果面d歷史真係無聽過乜滯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"其實都係一知半解<br />\n<br />\n去過新彊同西藏　聽過當地人講下故　自己又上網八卦<br />\n<br />\n唔好信哂"},{"pid":"e6c3bd9c5a77b9ac859b45c58c9099923d7a0b89","tid":1018040,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bc2d5058e9de5780e5da03daf7d0ad621f94e216","tid":1018040,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b78ce8634685959c0aaee4507cdad2981622bdba","tid":1018040,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T03:27:48.000Z","msg":"土耳其前身為　波斯＞阿拉伯帝國＞帕木兒＞鄂圖曼帝國<br />\n主要為伊斯蘭教　跟古代中國有大量商貿合作　<br />\n新彊位於兩強之間　鮮有相犯<br />\n<br />\n土耳其　現在為新彊發聲，主要原因乃宗教　非血緣關係"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:09:44.000Z","msg":"但係佢地d輪廓好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:21:17.000Z","msg":"其實唔多似　維族人白啲　阿拉伯人黃黃黑黑咁<br />\n<br />\n土耳其以前係拜占庭帝國　位於歐亞交界處　信東正教<br />\n但同時容許　羅馬正教　同伊斯蘭教徒生活<br />\n　<br />\n所以土耳其依個國家嘅人雜到九彩　佢撐新彊都係宗教姐"},{"pid":"fac9307319183055527ddeb701f32dc40df92081","tid":1018040,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e997ba493afebc56f51df7a108708816b23c1dbe","tid":1018040,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:23:15.000Z","msg":"維吾爾族係中國人既其中一個民族"},{"pid":"069af2d31b2dc3c33474f9f9b04c616a0845f367","tid":1018040,"uid":233228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:29:57.000Z","msg":"本來新彊民族性就比其他地方複雜<br />\n就算係維族統治一樣會有內亂<br />\n因為裏面仲有藏族蒙族哈薩克族漢族<br />\n二千幾年以黎勢力都係咁平均<br />\n冇咗滿清中共我諗新彊會同阿富汗一樣"},{"pid":"d582fe31021e0dc08fa8d7c6d82e2a3a9612c173","tid":1018040,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:32:23.000Z","msg":"當年乾隆搶咗香香公主種下仇恨"},{"pid":"9ffcf9bc8483e0349c62ce62f1aec90ad4a804f9","tid":1018040,"uid":181133,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"突厥=Turkish<br />\n新疆=東突厥斯坦"},{"pid":"b8d939aa91b5630a5f03a03a812c17679a222fbf","tid":1018040,"uid":57214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:43:57.000Z","msg":"東土耳其<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2c/Kokbayraq_flag.svg/800px-Kokbayraq_flag.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F2%2F2c%2FKokbayraq_flag.svg%2F800px-Kokbayraq_flag.svg.png&h=08c86d4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e769bd42535a080bec9da75f23201fad61bca309","tid":1018040,"uid":44646,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"9ffcf9bc8483e0349c62ce62f1aec90ad4a804f9","tid":1018040,"uid":181133,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"突厥=Turkish<br />\n新疆=東突厥斯坦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"新疆維人同土耳其人血緣好疏<br />\n但語言同屬突厥語，據講仍可溝通<br />\n土耳其一直有泛突厥主義，<br />\n自然支持維人。<br />\n<br />\n晚清左宗棠成功鎮壓回亂<br />\n民國時代，新疆大致上由軍閥盛世才控制<br />\n名義上奉國府為中央<br />\n抗日時新疆就無咩出力<br />\n而且實際上受蘇聯影響較大<br />\n<br />\n國共內戰時，新疆少數民族亦再試圖建國<br />\n同國軍打之餘，亦屠過漢人鄉村<br />\n但史達林反對新疆少數民族建國<br />\n迫佢地同中共合併<br />\n(班代表去北京時，「飛機意外」死曬)<br />\n之後維人叛軍合併入解放軍<br />\n(以上可SEARCH三區革命)<br />\n<br />\n中共就繼承清---民國，領有新疆<br />\n又係高壓、懷柔+移民咁啦"},{"pid":"dac98f36a7a7386bf64d6ecb8d8c8ff12b9ee0db","tid":1018040,"uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e769bd42535a080bec9da75f23201fad61bca309","tid":1018040,"uid":44646,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"9ffcf9bc8483e0349c62ce62f1aec90ad4a804f9","tid":1018040,"uid":181133,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"突厥=Turkish<br />\n新疆=東突厥斯坦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T05:52:36.000Z",